   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Humanitarian Response to the floods in Riosucio and Carmen in Choco</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Following the floods in Bajo Atrato region (Choco, Colombia) which affected more than 40.000 people, an assessment identified the need for a humanitarian response in the municipalities of&#xA0; Carmen del Darien and Riosucio. This project will provide humanitarian assistance in water and sustainable livelihoods to 29.000 people living in urban and rural areas.</narrative>
